{"tid":329264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"互打飛機可轉運？男心中疙瘩藏一年　受不了拿刀刺友","createTime":"2017-07-20T08:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T03:25:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fec03ee2d8b861890bf08f12db7ed9cb9a65cbe7","tid":329264,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:38:39.000Z","msg":"社會中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n互「打手槍」可以改運？台中一名34歲吳姓男子曾想要祭改改運，誰知陳姓友人知道後，向他表示<span style=\"color: red;\">「只要兩人互打手槍就能幫他改運」</span>，吳男當下順從陳男說法，真的<span style=\"color: red;\">在某廟寺廂房內互打手槍</span>，但事後越想越不對勁，向陳男討解釋，但陳男卻說不出來，吳男氣不過直接拿刀砍人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2016/09/23/656515-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F09%2F23%2F656515-XXL.jpg&h=aef7906e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲兩人在寺廟內打手槍。（示意圖／攝影者hiroooooki, Flickr CC License）</span><br />\n<br />\n根據起訴書，吳男跟陳男因在台中市外埔區某廟當清潔工相識，當時吳男拿著衣服打算祭改，陳男得知後，<span style=\"color: red;\">說吳男是「卡到陰」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，要兩人互打手槍來改運，吳男當下信了陳男，真的與他在寺廟廂房內互打手槍，陳男還將精液抹在他身上</span>，但事後吳男越想越不對，向陳男數度討要說法，但陳男總推諉或置之不理，讓吳男懷恨在心一年多，心中陰影一直無法除去。<br />\n<br />\n吳男一直覺得自己被耍，忍受不了心中疙瘩，持長約22公分的鏟刀就衝到陳男住處，要求他出來解釋，但陳男依舊拒絕，吳男一氣之下就往陳男頸刺了5刀，導致陳男失血過多，送醫仍不治身亡。陳妻看到此景嚇到趕快報警，但緊張到說不清楚，吳男於是搶過電話，向警方坦承殺人，台中地檢署依殺人等罪起訴吳男。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=274751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D274751&d=8LRx0u3ywii7NK47kZIC5zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=cbe83a1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D274751&h=769949c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=274751</a>"},{"pid":"83da552207895cff71a4cd781c2e4ec07baf8343","tid":329264,"uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"想和你互射，有錯嗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2009039c54d27fc98680b66f33f3a03c886db3e","tid":329264,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fcfaaf97c3d54cf20c77b21fbc525365ca2d02f3","tid":329264,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc0ccbbd0cb9f10f58c3d77ebcd348c60ca7f0d","tid":329264,"uid":19360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0527b75dfbfee2d736f60a6e0d03a1d2788ec19b","tid":329264,"uid":36029,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"轉危為gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f27441dab28d64a035f1df1cb79c864c5f3c9c","tid":329264,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"Gayyyyyyyyyyyy"},{"pid":"8f643043305b64bf276ef93966a8acb1fe180f53","tid":329264,"uid":17531,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16fb7cc625d956b8be93c613b9f739c611c93c15","tid":329264,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"但做對好兄弟又如此相愛"},{"pid":"ed3444ff05c0b7d5189d739321b46d9feaf758ef","tid":329264,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉危為gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji